episodes.title: CBS EVENING NEWS (4/11/1989): Mass grave involving Satanic cult found in Matamoros, Mexico
episodes.description: CBS EVENING NEWS (4/11/1989): Mass grave involving Satanic cult found in Matamoros, Mexico; Oliver North criminal trial - did North profit?; Latest accusations against Pete Rose; 10 million+ gallons of crude oil in Alaska waters - Exxon's response is seen as slow and callous
